@lv3pro Worldwide PSA 🔈🔈🔈#Miami 🏝

We’d like to officially welcome Allison_cuts to the #LV3family 🙏🏽

Allison is an up & coming barber that has proven her worth in a short period of time in our industry! Were excited to have her join our movement! Catch her making her debut on our Main Stage at the @connecticutbarberexpo 🤘

From our First Ambassador In 2013 @los_cut_it to our Newest Raising Star Allison_cuts ⭐️ #BarberssignBarbers 

@lv3pro is in FULL EFFECT 🚀🚀🚀 

#StayTuned for New Official Releases of our extended #LV3 Family Worldwide! 

L3VEL3™️ 
Make sure to hashtag #LV3 #L3VEL3 to selected as a LV3™️ Brand ambassador

LV3.com
